      "file_path": "robot/testsuites/vnf-orchestration-ovp.robot",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 377,
      "message": "The existing preload structure uses jinja templates to build the preload. When people run this testsuite they won't have jinja templates, instead they'll have preload json files. I can add both options to sdnc_interface so you can use jinja or use an already created preload.",
