      "file_path": "robot/testsuites/vnf-orchestration-ovp.robot",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 431,
      "message": "Mainly because I didn't want VNF owners to have to create one before they run the test, but the SDC orchestration flow requires the service mapping to be there. The testsuite is built to handle an arbitrary VNF, so rather than require VNF owners to build one for each VNF they try to orchestrate, I'm just adding it at runtime.",
